## FastAPI Rules

- Use `pydantic` models for request validation and responses.
- Define routes in logically grouped routers (e.g., `users.py`, `items.py`).
- Apply response models explicitly for docs and consistency.
- Include example inputs/outputs for each endpoint in comments or docstrings.
